Package restapi

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AADMService
    A service that returns the abstract application deployment model in JSON format.
    AbstractService  
    AttributeService
    A service that returns the attributes of a single TOSCA node
    CapabilityService
    A service that returns the capabilities of a single TOSCA resource in JSON format
    InterfaceService
    A service that returns the interfaces of a single TOSCA node
    NodeService
    A service that returns all the known TOSCA nodes in the KB
    OptimizationService
    A service that submits the abstract application deployment model to the Knowledge Base and returns applicable optimizations according to the capabilities.
    PropertyService
    A service that returns the properties of a single TOSCA node
    RequirementService
    A service that returns the requirements of a single TOSCA node
    SubmitRMService
    A service that submits the resource model to the Knowledge Base.
    SubmitService
    A service that submits the abstract application deployment model to the Knowledge Base.
    ValidRequirementNodesService
    A service that returns nodes that satisfy a certain requirement of a node template of type nodeType.
